Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.44,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Flowing water has no form.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:05.33,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A blowing wind can't be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:07.28,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All cases can be freely deduced!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.28,0:00:09.05,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today, we're at a coffee shop by a road on a hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.05,0:00:11.24,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Was it an accident or a case that came flying in?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:12.83,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:14.63,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.43,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:48.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't walk another step.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:50.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:52.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a little further...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to Doc's map, it's right around this curve coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.44,0:01:56.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can do it, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:01.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, maybe taking the bus would've been faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:02.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:04.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going to be treated to lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so if we take the bus it would render everything meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:08.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean you just wanted to save bus fare?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.55,0:02:12.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What a tight-fisted brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:23.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... It's supposed to be around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mitsuhiko, isn't that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:36.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"P-e-a-c-h S-u-n-d-a-y..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:37.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the place after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.16,0:02:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you can read English?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm bilingual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.71,0:02:47.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's go inside. I'm starved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.49,0:02:48.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:02:59.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Boys, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to meet with Dr. Agasa here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:03.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:04.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- Right.\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm starved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hi there, welcome to our shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:15.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dr. Agasa called me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he'll be a little late, so eat anything you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That looks yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:24.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, ladies first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Of course! Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:28.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:34.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Ohara. I have a reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, please come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They say the house specialty is great, it's the peach sundae.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the owner's original.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll have that, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:43.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:46.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What would you like, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same as the rest of you is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, four peach sundaes please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That looks yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- It's really yummy!\N- It sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:02.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you gonna eat, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take it, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:08.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be a waste if the ice cream were to melt...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that? Leaflets again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a rush job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:16.50,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kazuo Ohara (52)\NOhara Design —\hPresident
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:16.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're going to be passing it out at the shopping center {any better wording for shoutengai?} this coming Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should just refuse such a cheap-paying job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:20.79,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Toru Aida (35)\NOhara Design —\hDesigner
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:20.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:25.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the kind of job that leads to a stable income! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:32.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you think about the you-know-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:35.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times you ask me,\Nmy answer will not change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it money you want?\NIf so, I'll increase the amount...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:41.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think you can,\Nwith what work you're doing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe not just yet,\Nbut I promise that someday I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There you go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:47.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you do something about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:49.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk about persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:54.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to spend the rest of my life making leaflets!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:58.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Working with you is ruining my talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:04:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:02.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll bet you don't have any on the pamphlets
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:04.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,of the resort hotel that I'm asking you to work on this time.{?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, as for that, I'll take the job as pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:12.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't handle it anyway if I leave, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I promise to finish these leaflets before I leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:23.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get started. You're in a hurry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:29.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:44.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:46.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:51.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko, what's your second recommendation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll get a stomachache if you eat too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:55.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:00.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:02.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I gotta go to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta, someone's in the restroom right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Somebody's inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:16.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:17.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's indeed worth recommending.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:20.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Genta, someone was inside, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:21.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know who's in there,\Nbut he doesn't answer when I knock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- I'm gonna explode...\N- Oh, he just came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:29.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, a customer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:33.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yay, I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:36.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're ordering seconds, get me some too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:40.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:44.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's using his right hand this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:46.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's ambidextrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Dr. Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.83,0:06:53.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:54.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're all digging in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, eat all you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:06:59.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won the raffle at the shopping center!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:01.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright then, I'll take...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:05.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a hot fudge sundae, custard à la mode\Nand strawberry shortcake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's your stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine, just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at that bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it is. It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I dropped my lighter. I'll go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:32.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want it done by sundown. I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:34.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:42.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, whatcha having?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll have coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:46.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that you just happened to leave your seat, so you were spared?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I just happened to go to the restroom to look for my lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness you were spared...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:22.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're the president of Ohara Design.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The office is located at the top of the hill, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:28.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found the driver of the truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:35.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you park your car part-way up the hill, like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and make your delivery?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:50.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I usually park on a flat place uphill,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:51.06,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Jiro Kobayashi (25)\NExpress Delivery Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but that car was parked here today,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:55.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I had no choice but to park in front of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:59.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I made sure my emergency brake was engaged,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and had the gear in reverse just to be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:05.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I went to the site right away
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:09.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and checked the driver's seat, but the emergency brake was disengaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:12.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible! Please check more carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know I pulled my emergency brake and engaged it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:16.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course he's lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was my precious right-hand man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:27.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without him, my company is finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Did someone die?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:31.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:33.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Segawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:36.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:41.11,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Michiko Segawa (46)\NOhara Design —\hClerk
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:38.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we don't deposit the money today,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:41.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they're going to stop shipment of the goods!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:42.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this is no time for something that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:48.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} passed away...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was in an accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:52.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:04.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Strange. What could that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:08.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! This place is off-limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:19.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forgot something in the restroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:24.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He was licking his finger when he first came out of the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:26.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I wonder if he got hurt in the restroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:29.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:46.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Blood stains?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:53.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}These are traces of a hand touching the frame from outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:10:59.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.29,0:11:03.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The blood got here when he came back from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.19,0:11:06.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's why there was no answer when Genta knocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:11.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ohara{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} wasn't in the restroom then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:17.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He hurt his left hand when he was outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:23.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's why he held the pencil in his right after coming back...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:28.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But where did he go,\Nand what was he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:44.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Before the accident, Ohara{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}\Nseemed very concerned about the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:48.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Did he have to go out at a certain time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:50.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan, where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just went to get something I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:07.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does anyone remember at what time the accident occurred?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:10.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About 2:10, right after Dr. Agasa got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,2:10...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:15.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's one at 2:07...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:17.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:22.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what route the bus that left here just before the accident took?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it should be coming back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to make a circuit from the complex back to the shopping center.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:38.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why was that bus stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the end of the line,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:43.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so the buses take a break for 5 to 10\Nminutes to get back on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:56.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do we have a case?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:59.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No fair, Conan! You're always hogging the clues!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'd like to ask you kids some questions too,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so come here, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:15.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:19.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Piano wire?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:24.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Aha! I've figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is a homicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And the killer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:30.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm sure it's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:41.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have some urgent business to attend to,\Nso I'd like to be excused for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:47.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to go make a bank transfer to one of my clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:51.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,30 minutes—no, 20 minutes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:55.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has he been questioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:58.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, briefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:00.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you can go, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:06.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If he's released, he'll go and get rid of all the evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:08.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a homicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:14.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move your lips like always for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:17.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:19.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:22.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I can't have you leave just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:26.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a murder case!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:34.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Agasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:38.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will outsiders stay out of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it. Let's at least hear him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:43.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agasa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, do you have a lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:45.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I not only have a lead, I have proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ohara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have proof that you are the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.11,0:14:54.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:58.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it, this is an accident caused by the carelessness of the driver
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:59.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,whose truck crashed into the shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:01.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let us hear, Agasa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:08.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well. Then first, let me explain the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a busy man! I don't have time\Nto waste listening to a made-up story!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:16.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ohara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:20.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll just be a short while, so let's hear him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:24.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ohara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you parked your car\Nat the top of the hill
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,where the delivery truck always parks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:35.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you asked Aida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to come with you\Nto the coffee shop at the bottom of the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then you made him sit by the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:40.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so that he couldn't see the slope from his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:42.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't make him sit by the window so that he couldn't see the slope!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:51.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The place he sat just happened to be by the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.25,0:15:56.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you left a while later,\Nin the middle of negotiation,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:15:59.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,pretending to go to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:03.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't pretending! I really went to the restroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,0:16:11.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} here says he kept knocking on the door, but you didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:15.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! My stomach was so sore, I thought I'd die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:16.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:20.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back then, you snuck out of the restroom window,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:22.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and went over to the delivery truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You placed a wooden wedge that you had set up beforehand
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in front of the front tires of the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:34.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would I do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:39.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a trick to make it look like you weren't committing the crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:43.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You attached piano wire to the wooden wedge,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then tied it to the back of the bus\Nwhich was parked there for time adjustment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you shifted the gear of the delivery truck to neutral,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and released the emergency brake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:59.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then returned to the coffee shop as if nothing had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the time came\Nand the bus started to move,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the wedge would come off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:12.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, the delivery truck would roll down the hill all by itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:16.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All you had to do next was to wait for the bus to pass the coffee shop
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and get out of the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:21.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,by pretending to go to the restroom to look for your lighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The thing that was shimmering at the back of the bus
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:29.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was the piano wire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:32.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. And that wedge is right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:34.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:37.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:38.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:44.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just a plain piece of wood...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wooden wedge is dragged along by the bus,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and shatters as it bounces on the pavement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what's left of the wedge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The car, which was accelerating because the road was on a hill,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:57.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,crashed into the window of the coffee shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:18:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and burst inside, just as you had planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was hit and killed by the truck from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's say... Let's say the trick is as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:19.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But do you have proof that I did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Proof? I sure do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:28.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was your mistake: you hurt your finger tying the piano wire to the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:33.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My hand got stuck on the restroom doorknob!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The delivery truck can be operated one-handed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:40.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so you didn't leave any blood stains there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when you re-entered through the restroom window,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you touched it and left blood stains on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's some blood on the inside of the restroom window.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.39,0:18:59.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After returning from the restroom,\Nyou continued making arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:04.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since you hurt your left hand,\Nyou held the pencil in your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan witnessed you licking your left hand occasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:11.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I hurt my finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:22.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But like I just said, I scratched it on the doorknob.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:24.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can something like that be considered proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can it, officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:27.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-He's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:28.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, if you insist I'm the killer,\Nshow me concrete evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:36.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:45.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a glove with a strange pattern in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this, Ohara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the piano wire on the bus is checked,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,your blood should also be detected on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:11.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blood stains from your wound in the restroom
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the blood stains on the glove in the car should match exactly!{bluffed this a bit, couldn't make sense of either}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blood stain on the frame of the restroom window
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:19.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,shows that you held the frame from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, your blood stains are also on the piano wire tied to the bus...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How are you going to explain all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:35.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about it, Ohara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:41.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I did him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:51.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aida dared to forget everything I did for him until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:55.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and betrayed me by saying he was going to quit working for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:21:00.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he were to quit, my company would go bankrupt...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.81,0:21:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it were going to go bankrupt anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured I should kill him\Nand make it look like an accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:11.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and at least get a hold of his\Nlife insurance money as compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, I hadn't made my mind up until we were at the coffee shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:24.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he had the nerve to say he was going to take away a big job that I found as retirement pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:28.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What a thing to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:31.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:10.76,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Peach Sunday —\hRenovated and Reopening"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Agasa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.10,0:23:18.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, my innocence has been proven.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.17,0:23:23.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem, no big thing, I can handle things like this with my hands tied behind my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.48,0:23:26.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am the one who taught the famous high-school detective Shin'ichi Kudo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:31.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the skills of being a detective, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.40,0:23:33.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:35.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Geez. You sure can talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.78,0:23:37.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.55,0:23:40.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.50,0:23:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's dated 10 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.97,0:23:54.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is 10 years before Misaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} got married!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.30,0:23:58.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.53,0:24:06.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could there be more than one killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.46,0:24:09.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is this a piece of?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.20,0:24:12.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just as I thought... This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.48,0:24:18.53,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.53,0:24:23.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Bust
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.73,0:24:25.60,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, a dignified tale!
